MANDATORY: After every change to the codebase, update CLAUDE_CONTEXT.md before considering the task complete. Update the relevant sections (player state if types changed, merchants if inventory changed, schema if database changed, file map if new files, weapon system if `uoData`/equip/combat changed, etc.), add a new entry to the Session Log at the top of section 16, move completed items from Next Up to Completed Milestones when done, and update the Last Updated date in the header. Commit CLAUDE_CONTEXT.md in the same git commit as the code changes.

FILE URL LIST RULE: Every time you create a new file that Claude would need to read (any .ts, .tsx, .mjs, .js, .css file outside of node_modules, .next, and build folders), you must add its raw GitHub URL to the 📋 PASTE THESE INTO CHAT block in CLAUDE_CONTEXT.md. The URL format is:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/scotch-glass/living-eamon/main/[path/to/file]

Also remove any file from that list if it is deleted.
This list must always reflect every current file Claude needs to read to understand the codebase.
